00:39:38.817 --> 00:39:39.987
¿Debería ir?

00:39:40.288 --> 00:39:42.428
Hola, Nan Young.

00:39:42.828 --> 00:39:44.027
Metí la pata...

00:39:44.458 --> 00:39:47.797
